Author: unicorn11
Title: [ANN][ICO][PreSale] Paytailor - Disrupting card payment infrastructure
Body: guys, great product!  I was going through the materials and spotted IoT payments as well. Could you please specify, are there any limitations to which machines you can integrate with the payment?

Author: Paytailor Official
Title: [ANN][ICO][PreSale] Paytailor - Disrupting card payment infrastructure
Body: We can basically integrate to any machine, which has internet connection and we can also make a 3G connection. Machine in the video was a Palma machine. But we have made gadget for Jura machine as well.

Author: unicorn11
Title: [ANN][ICO][PreSale] Paytailor - Disrupting card payment infrastructure
Body: GREAT! Just that I get it right - you can take any vending machine or equipment (?) and either connect it with payment via existing internet connection or if one does not have it, add this connection? How complicated it is to add the connection? My interest concerns the scaling.  Thanks!

Author: Paytailor Official
Title: [ANN][ICO][PreSale] Paytailor - Disrupting card payment infrastructure
Body: It depends a complexity of the machine or a system, but couple of weeks usually. After that controllers can be produced quite easily.
